@startuml
skinparam componentStyle rectangle
title Smartcard / TPM credential isolation

actor User
node "Client workstation" {
  [LSASS] as LSASS
  [Cryptographic API\n(CNG / minidriver)] as CAPI
}

package "Secure cryptoprocessor" {
  database "Protected key store" as KS {
    [Private key\n(non-exportable)] as PK
  }
  [On-board crypto engine] as ENGINE
  [PIN / anti-hammering\ncounter] as PIN
}

User --> PIN : unlock with PIN / biometric
LSASS --> CAPI
CAPI --> ENGINE : "sign(challenge)"
ENGINE --> PK : use key in place
ENGINE --> CAPI : signature
PK -[hidden]-> KS

note bottom of ENGINE
  Private key never leaves the
  cryptoprocessor. Only signatures
  and the public certificate exit.
end note
@enduml
